latestPosts.caption:
Tagged a couple of Makeup artists I look up to, and genuinely support❤️ we might not know each other personally, but you’re doing a Fab job!

To anyone who still thinks makeup artistry isn’t a “real job”: 

It’s real when we wake up at 4am for bridal bookings.
It’s real when we spend hours perfecting every detail to make someone feel confident and beautiful. 
It’s real when our hands ache, our backs hurt, and we still keep smiling for our clients. 

This is not just a job. It’s passion, precious, and people.
And just because it looks effortless…doesn’t mean it is.

Kudos to MUA’s of our industry❤️ 
.
.
.
.
